fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.data.types

Interface IArrayType

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICellStructure, IType

    public interface IArrayType
extends ICellStructure, IType
    Cell data type representing an embedded set of child items attached as an array to a parent item.

    Thread safety: implementations are required to be immutable and therefore completely thread-safe.

    1.0
